&lt;li&gt;Long-Term Career Opportunities: Build a lasting career with Apex, supported by tuition assistance and ongoing professional development.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Purpose-Driven Work: Make a real difference by helping protect and improve water quality in your local communities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
